The paper discusses the use of LSTM and CNN networks in solving problems related to images and sequences, which are common topics in the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also discusses preprocessing techniques for effective analysis of the data, which is a common topic in the machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
